title: Evanescence Vino's Performance
description:
This is a performance of Evanescence at Vino's in Little Rock, Arkansas "1999". The setlist of this show contains...

1.) Intro
2.) Whisper
3.) Imaginary
4.) Where Will You Go
5.) **Unknown Song**
6.) Exodus
7.) Give Unto Me
8.) Don't Fear The Reaper
9.) Understanding
10.) Lies
11.) Solitude

This is a DVD rip of the performance, which means these files are in .vob extentions.
